Author: donout_disturb
Text: I can relate. Sometimes I binge to get that itch out of my head and move on. When I get that urge it's very difficult for me to escape it or ignore it, and it makes impossible for me to focus on anything else, so I might as well do it, calm my ass down and move on. Not the best way to do it, but honestly I cannot spend all my life focusing on my ed and fighting with my head, I'd rather just give in.
